{"tid":2216582,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"林鄭月娥稱不吐不快　指警方的修訂為傳媒提供特別安排","createTime":"2020-09-24T20:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T02:38:28.000Z","uid":130626,"like":1,"dislike":69,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"dc9a1226fee831f575f5ffabb05c38c15a6f36b1","tid":2216582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:41:09.000Z","msg":"警方將《警察通例》中「傳媒代表」的定義，修訂為已登記政府新聞處新聞發布系統的傳媒機構。<br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥在社交網頁形容，警隊採用「客觀、開放、一視同仁的服務平台」，界定傳媒代表，為傳媒在行動中提供特別安排，包括可進入封鎖區內採訪，一如獲安排出席記者招待會或活動做採訪，反問「怎會是打壓新聞自由或篩選記者」；又說《基本法》保障香港居民享有言論、新聞、出版等的自由，不會改變。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥說，政府新聞處新聞發布系統，事實上可以說是整個政府與傳媒的聯繫平台，見到不少新聞仍圍繞事件，感到不吐不快。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551513-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551513-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7e5f0fc1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1551513-20200925.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=f7b0640e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1551513-20200925.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"c0dfc6b295e8244b9bc7f515e4d8b808377998d1","tid":2216582,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":33,"score":-33,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:42:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jUnm9B4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjUnm9B4.png&h=5d4ad6cb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4haTgg5.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4haTgg5.png&h=732d5ee6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"474e2e1ecba07fb260e4082ecd78ae8a2c845f25","tid":2216582,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T21:06:55.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"cc9c55a3f726c623345be8555fb3a229fa681673","tid":2216582,"uid":36296,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"c